        <para>The Tamboti search interface does not work with Internet Explorer 6 and 7. The Tamboti
            editor does not work with Internet Explorer 6, 7, and 8. If you are running Windows XP, you cannot use Internet Explorer to access all functions of Tamboti.
            You may, however, use Internet Explorer 8 to <emphasis>search</emphasis> Tamboti.</para>
        <para>Most browsers have accelerated their update cycle.
            This may cause problems with breaking browser versions. If you run into a problem, please open a <ulink href="http://kjc-sv007.kjc.uni-heidelberg.de/helpdesk/open.php">ticket</ulink>.</para>
